logText: I was driving down I35 when I happened across this beautiful city in Texas.
I came here because a friend recommended it to me. I have since unfriended them.
This town was very fun to be in.
Birds here, birds there, birds everywhere.
When I visted, my experience differed from what I thought it was going to be like.
I flew into this city for a concert, and ended up staying an extra night!
I lived here for 25 years, and found everything I ever needed.
I've lived under a rock my entire life.
I grew up here and held many fond memories of my high school.
This city is one of the worst. I wouldn't recommend it.
